Name: To The Top
About the game: Accompany Maya, a mysterious hooded woman, and her little companion on an adventure where the only thing that matters is reaching the top. GET TO THE TOP To The Top is a randomly generated 2D platform game with pixel style artwork. Move, Shoot and Use Power Ups to reach the top of each level while battling and dogging your enemies. Do your best to finish each level an get the code to access each scenario! Enjoy the music of the talented Jake Altmann as you progress through this dangerous futuristic world in either Casual or Normal mode.
